{"tid":304954,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人租緊$6k樓下嘅樓/套房？","createTime":"2017-07-01T09:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T12:23:24.000Z","uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e951993f3f6bc58c65270e9109c460d2aecee5c","tid":304954,"uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T09:59:11.000Z","msg":"想出黎住，而加每個月比緊4k屋企，出黎住就唔比咁多<br />\n<br />\n月入25k，灣仔區番工<br />\n<br />\n想搵d 100-150尺左右嘅樓，邊到易搵？<br />\n唐樓唔緊要，乾淨就得。<br />\n<br />\n除左水電煤，仲有咩雜費？<br />\n<br />\n10k足唔足夠我每個月食、住、行？"},{"pid":"2928ed2ec589d12bf3c7c9ac14c0dc9dbc064fbb","tid":304954,"uid":1008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:01:52.000Z","msg":"出來住一定比多過四千，想清楚先好決定。"},{"pid":"c969002516b295cfd6524174e7ea1b59d2ae943d","tid":304954,"uid":63302,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:11:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a39bab4adbb755180549733f6b6e2d812728a181","tid":304954,"uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同我合租啦，700呎村屋，元朗，3k 一個月，一個鐘出中環</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係唔想番工搭咁耐車呀<br />\n<br />\n自己住仲要煮飯，搭咁耐車，我咩時間都冇晒"},{"pid":"1b21329bcf722358cf37e7fd138da9256a118437","tid":304954,"uid":1965,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出來住一定比多過四千，想清楚先好決定。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我預$10k 住、食、行，夠唔夠？"},{"pid":"8748a9797fb1cd406e3f4b601a7ba47df4f37048","tid":304954,"uid":102132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:17:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f7e40738f903b093092adb949ef7b12d9380ddf","tid":304954,"uid":44512,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T11:21:59.000Z","msg":"住一百尺既屋好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，舊年租過100尺左右既套房，真係床，廁所+一格仔地方活動。<br />\n<br />\n真係食野，玩電腦都係床到，最後租左兩三個月就頂唔順走左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵人夾租 租間大小小啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"